s["consumer-insights"]=make_skill("consumer-insights","Consumer Insights Generation","research","intermediate","medium","Use when generating consumer insights from data, identifying patterns, or translating research into actionable recommendations.","You are a consumer research specialist with expertise in insight generation, data synthesis, and translating findings into marketing action.","## Insights Generation Workflow\n\n- [ ] 1. Data synthesis: Combine data from {{data_sources}}\n- [ ] 2. Pattern identification: Find recurring themes and patterns\n- [ ] 3. Insight formulation: Transform patterns into actionable insights\n- [ ] 4. Validation: Cross-check insights against known facts\n- [ ] 5. Prioritization: Rank insights by business impact\n- [ ] 6. Action planning: Translate insights into specific actions","## Consumer Insights: {{client_name}}\n\n### Insight Sources: {{data_sources}}\n\n### Key Insights\n\n#### Insight 1: [Title]\n**What we found:**\n[Observation from data]\n\n**Why it matters:**\n[Business implication]\n\n**What to do:**\n[Specific action]\n\n**Confidence:** [High/Medium/Low]\n\n---\n\n#### Insight 2: [Title]\n[Same structure]\n\n### Insight-Action Matrix\n| Insight | Action | Owner | Timeline | Impact |\n|---------|--------|-------|----------|--------|\n| | | | | |\n\n### Surprising Findings\n[Unexpected discoveries that challenge assumptions]\n\n### Confirmed Assumptions\n[Things we thought were true, now validated]","[{name:client_name,type:string,required:true,desc:Client name},{name:data_sources,type:string,required:true,desc:Data sources used},{name:research_objective,type:string,required:false,desc:Research objective}]",[{"step":1,"name":"Data Synthesis","action":"Combine data sources","verify":"All relevant data included"},{"step":2,"name":"Pattern ID","action":"Find recurring themes","verify":"Patterns are statistically valid"},{"step":3,"name":"Insight Formulation","action":"Transform patterns into insights","verify":"Insights are surprising and meaningful"},{"step":4,"name":"Validation","action":"Cross-check insights","verify":"Insights are credible"},{"step":5,"name":"Prioritization","action":"Rank by impact","verify":"Priorities are justified"},{"step":6,"name":"Action Planning","action":"Translate to actions","verify":"Actions are specific"}],["All relevant data sources used","Patterns are statistically valid","Insights are surprising and meaningful","Insights are validated","Priorities are business-impact driven","Actions are specific and measurable"],"analytics","spreadsheet",["atlas"],"consumer-insights","research","analytics","Generates actionable consumer insights from data synthesis with insight-action matrices and prioritization.")
s["consumer-journey-mapping"]=make_skill("consumer-journey-mapping","Consumer Journey Mapping","research","intermediate","medium","Use when mapping customer journeys, identifying touchpoints, or understanding the path to purchase.","You are a CX strategist specializing in customer journey mapping, touchpoint analysis, and experience design.","## Journey Mapping Workflow\n\n- [ ] 1. Persona definition: Define the customer persona for {{persona_name}}\n- [ ] 2. Journey phases: Define stages from awareness to advocacy\n- [ ] 3. Touchpoint mapping: Map all touchpoints at each stage\n- [ ] 4. Emotion tracking: Track emotional state through journey\n- [ ] 5. Pain point identification: Identify friction points\n- [ ] 6. Opportunity mapping: Identify improvement opportunities","## Consumer Journey Map: {{persona_name}}\n\n### Industry: {{industry}}\n\n### Journey Stages\n\n#### 1. AWARENESS\n**What they do:**\n[Discovery activities]\n\n**Touchpoints:**\n| Touchpoint | Channel | Owner | Experience |\n|------------|---------|-------|-------------|\n| | | | |\n\n**Emotion:** [Emotional state at this stage]\n\n#### 2. CONSIDERATION\n[Same structure]\n\n#### 3. DECISION\n[Same structure]\n\n#### 4. PURCHASE\n[Same structure]\n\n#### 5. RETENTION\n[Same structure]\n\n#### 6. ADVOCACY\n[Same structure]\n\n### Pain Points Summary\n| Pain Point | Stage | Severity | Impact |\n|------------|-------|----------|--------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Opportunity Register\n| Opportunity | Pain Point Addressed | Effort | Impact |\n|-------------|---------------------|--------|--------|\n| | | | |","[{name:persona_name,type:string,required:true,desc:Persona name},{name:industry,type:string,required:true,desc:Industry},{name:purchase_context,type:string,required:false,desc:Purchase context}]",[{"step":1,"name":"Persona Definition","action":"Define customer persona","verify":"Persona is specific"},{"step":2,"name":"Phase Definition","action":"Define journey stages","verify":"Stages cover full journey"},{"step":3,"name":"Touchpoint Mapping","action":"Map all touchpoints","verify":"All touchpoints included"},{"step":4,"name":"Emotion Tracking","action":"Track emotional state","verify":"Emotions are mapped to stages"},{"step":5,"name":"Pain Point ID","action":"Identify friction points","verify":"Pain points are real"},{"step":6,"name":"Opportunity Mapping","action":"Identify improvements","verify":"Opportunities address pain points"}],["Persona is specific and grounded","All journey stages covered","Touchpoints are comprehensive","Pain points are real and ranked","Opportunities are actionable","Journey map is validated with data"],"spreadsheet","presentation",["atlas","sage"],"journey-mapping","research","cx","Maps customer journeys with touchpoints, emotions, pain points, and improvement opportunities.")
s["contract-discussion"]=make_skill("contract-discussion","Contract Discussion","client-services","intermediate","medium","Use when preparing for contract negotiations, reviewing contract terms, or managing contract renewals.","You are a client services director with expertise in contract negotiation, commercial terms, and relationship management.","## Contract Discussion Workflow\n\n- [ ] 1. Terms review: Review current contract terms for {{client_name}}\n- [ ] 2. Market benchmarking: Benchmark terms against {{market_standards}}\n- [ ] 3. Client research: Understand client priorities and constraints\n- [ ] 4. Position development: Develop negotiation position for {{key_terms}}\n- [ ] 5. BATNA preparation: Prepare best alternative options\n- [ ] 6. Negotiation plan: Plan negotiation approach and contingencies","## Contract Negotiation: {{client_name}}\n\n### Contract Period: {{current_period}}\n### Negotiation Date: {{negotiation_date}}\n\n### Current Terms vs Market\n| Term | Current | Market | Gap |\n|------|---------|--------|-----|\n| Price | | | |\n| Duration | | | |\n| Scope | | | |\n| SLAs | | | |\n\n### Client Priorities\n| Priority | Level | Our Position |\n|----------|-------|--------------|\n| | | |\n\n### Our Priorities\n| Priority | Target | Walk-away point |\n|----------|--------|-----------------|\n| | | |\n\n### BATNA\n[Our best alternative if negotiation fails]\n\n### Negotiation Strategy\n| Topic | Opening Position | Target | Walk-away |\n|-------|-----------------|--------|-----------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Contingency Plans\n[What to do if negotiation goes wrong]","[{name:client_name,type:string,required:true,desc:Client name},{name:current_period,type:string,required:true,desc:Current contract period},{name:negotiation_date,type:string,required:true,desc:Negotiation date},{name:market_standards,type:string,required:false,desc:Market standards for comparison},{name:key_terms,type:string,required:false,desc:Key terms to negotiate}]",[{"step":1,"name":"Terms Review","action":"Review current contract terms","verify":"Terms are understood"},{"step":2,"name":"Benchmarking","action":"Benchmark against market","verify":"Benchmarks are current"},{"step":3,"name":"Client Research","action":"Understand client priorities","verify":"Priorities are known"},{"step":4,"name":"Position Development","action":"Develop negotiation position","verify":"Position is defensible"},{"step":5,"name":"BATNA Preparation","action":"Prepare alternatives","verify":"BATNA is real"},{"step":6,"name":"Negotiation Planning","action":"Plan approach","verify":"Plan is comprehensive"}],["Terms are thoroughly reviewed","Benchmarks are current and relevant","Client priorities are understood","Position is defensible","BATNA is real","Negotiation plan is comprehensive"],"document","spreadsheet",["sage"],"contract","negotiation","commercial","Prepares for contract negotiations with benchmarking, position development, and contingency planning.")
s["conversion-optimization"]=make_skill("conversion-optimization","Conversion Optimization","media","intermediate","medium","Use when optimizing conversion rates on landing pages, funnels, or digital properties.","You are a CRO specialist with expertise in conversion rate optimization, funnel analysis, and A/B testing.","## Conversion Optimization Workflow\n\n- [ ] 1. Funnel audit: Analyze current conversion funnel for {{property_name}}\n- [ ] 2. Data analysis: Review analytics data from {{data_sources}}\n- [ ] 3. User behavior analysis: Understand user behavior patterns\n- [ ] 4. Hypothesis development: Create optimization hypotheses\n- [ ] 5. Prioritization: Rank hypotheses by impact and effort\n- [ ] 6. Testing plan: Design tests for top hypotheses","## Conversion Optimization: {{property_name}}\n\n### Current Performance\n| Metric | Value | Industry Benchmark |\n|--------|-------|------------------|\n| Conversion rate | | |\n| Bounce rate | | |\n| Time on page | | |\n| Exit rate | | |\n\n### Funnel Analysis\n| Stage | Visitors | Drop-off | Drop-off Rate |\n|-------|---------|---------|---------------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Key Drop-off Points\n| Location | Drop-off Rate | Likely Cause | Confidence |\n|----------|--------------|--------------|------------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Optimization Hypotheses\n| Hypothesis | Page/Element | Expected Impact | Effort | Priority |\n|------------|--------------|-----------------|--------|----------|\n| | | | | |\n\n### Recommended Tests\n| Test | Hypothesis | Variant | Success Metric |\n|------|-----------|---------|---------------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Quick Wins\n[Low-effort, high-impact changes to implement immediately]","[{name:property_name,type:string,required:true,desc:Property/landing page name},{name:data_sources,type:string,required:true,desc:Analytics data sources},{name:current_conversion_rate,type:string,required:false,desc:Current conversion rate}]",[{"step":1,"name":"Funnel Audit","action":"Analyze current funnel","verify":"Funnel is mapped"},{"step":2,"name":"Data Analysis","action":"Review analytics data","verify":"Data is accurate"},{"step":3,"name":"Behavior Analysis","action":"Understand user patterns","verify":"Patterns are identified"},{"step":4,"name":"Hypothesis Development","action":"Create optimization hypotheses","verify":"Hypotheses are testable"},{"step":5,"name":"Prioritization","action":"Rank hypotheses","verify":"Priorities are justified"},{"step":6,"name":"Testing Plan","action":"Design tests","verify":"Tests are executable"}],["Funnel is accurately mapped","Drop-off points are identified","Hypotheses are testable","Priorities are impact-effort driven","Testing plan is executable","Quick wins are identified"],"analytics","spreadsheet",["dex","nova"],"conversion-optimization","cro","optimization","Optimizes conversion funnels with hypothesis development, prioritization, and testing plans.")

